Description: ==========================
        ReadMe for atreal.filecart
        ==========================
        
        Overview
        --------
        A cart for Plone to add file and download them in an archive.
        
        
        Authors
        -------
        :atReal Team [contact@atreal.net]
            Florent Michon [f10w]
        
        Credits
